Siong7-te3 Sou2 Beh Eng7 E5 Lang5 
Siong7-te3 sou2 beh eng7 e5 lang5 tioh8 chiau5-pi7 sim2-mih8 tiau5-kiaN7? Goa2 gian2-kiu3 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 chiu7 chhe7 tioh8 e7-bin7 sou2 kong2 e5 tiau5-kiaN7:
1. Tioh8 Chai Jin5-lui7 Kek8-ki5 Pai7-hoai7
Na7 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 hou7 lan2 khoaN3-beng5 jin5-lui7 e5 pun2-seng3 kek8-ki5 pai7-hoai7, lan2 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok chiu7 choe3 boe7 ku2-tng5. Lan2 tioh8 chai, jin5-lui7 i2-keng pho3-san2 lah. Lan2 tioh8 beng5-pek8, jin5-lui7 long2 si2 ti7 in e5 ke3-sit kap choe7-koa3, in-ui7 ti7 lan2 jiok8-the2 e5 lai7-bin7 bo5 ho2 ti7-teh. Lan2 tioh8 jim7-bat lang5 e5 sim i2-keng phaiN2 kau3 kek8-thau5.
Lan2 na7 siuN7 ti7 lang5 e5 sim-lai7 iau2 koh u7 tam7-poh8 seng3-kiat e5 oah8-mia7, lan2 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok chiu7 boe7 seng5-kong. In-ui7 an2-ni lan2 chiu7 oe7 toan3-teng7: Lan2 chi2-u7 chiong che tam7-poh8 e5 he2-chhiN------seng3-kiat e5 oah8-mia7 pun5 hou7 i toh8, i2-au7 ban7-su7 long2 oe7 ho2-se3 lah.
An2-ni chiu7 oan5-choan5 m7-bian2 teng5-thau5-siN, bo5 su-iau3 hoan2-hoe2, in-ui7 lang5 ki3-jian5 u7 oah8-mia7, chiu7 m7-bian2 koh chiap-siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 oah8-mia7; lang5 put-ko3 si7 poe7-gek8 ThiN-pe7 Siong7-te3 teh hong3-tong7, na7 hoe5-thau5 to3-lai5 chiu7 ho2! Sou2-i2 thoan5-kau3-chia2 e5 kang-chok chiu7-si7 khng3 lang5 180 tou7 e5 kai2-pian3, to3-tng2 lai5 chhe7 Siong7-te3 .
Chit khoan2 e5 khoaN3-hoat ia7 si7 an2-ni kong2, lan2 long2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5. Ki5-sit8, che kap Seng3-keng e5 ka3-si7 u7 cheng-chha. Lan2 na7 iau2-be7 teng5-thau5-siN, chiu7-si7 Sat-tan3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, oan5-choan5 m7-si7 siok8 ti7 Siong7-te3 ke-lai7 e5 lang5 , chi2-u7 tioh8 teng5-thau5-siN chiah oe7 hou7 lan2 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5. Sou2-i2 lan2 tioh8 jim7-bat jin5-lui7 si7 oan5-choan5 pai7-hoai7, tioh8 chai lang5 i2-keng si2, tit-tioh8 oah8-mia7 chiah oe7 koh-oah8 khi2-lai5, ka-ki7 oan5-choan5 bo5 ng3-bang7, chi2-u7 Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 kiu3 i. Che si7 chin iau3-kin2 e5 tiau5-tiau7, thoan5-kau3-chia2 na7 bo5 tit-tioh8, chiu7 boe7 seng5-kong.
2. Tioh8 Jim7-bat Siong7-te3 E5 Kiu3-un Chiau5-chng5
Jin5-lui7 sui-jian5 kek8-ki5 pai7-hoai7, na7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiu3-un chiau5-chng5, oe7 kai2-koat lang5 e5 su-iau3. OaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, Siong7-te3 u7 i-ti7 e5 pan7-hoat, I u7 chiau5-chng5 e5 chun2-pi7, beh hou7 lang5 chhut-si2 jip8-oah8. Ui7-tioh8 kek8-ki5 pai7-hoai7 e5 jin5-lui7, chiu7-si7 si2 ti7 in e5 ke3-sit kap choe7-koa3 e5, Siong7-te3 u7 pi7-pan7 beh chin2-kiu3 lang5 .
Ti7 1900 goa7 ni5 cheng5, tui3 I e5 tok8-siN KiaN2, lan2 e5 Chu2, I u7 pi7-pan7; sou2-i2 li2, goa2 teh choe3 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok, tioh8 chai-iaN2 lang5 i2-keng si2 ti7 in e5 ke3-sit kap choe7-koa3, oan5-choan5 bo5 pan7-hoat, pun2-sin bo5 ng3-bang7. Koh jin5-lui7 khak-sit8 pho3-san2, na7-si7 lan2 tioh8 beng5-pek8, lan2 u7 eng5-kng e5 Hok-im, chit ui7 ki5-biau7 e5 Kiu3-chu2 u7 siuN7 boe7 kau3 e5 pi7-pan7------oan5-choan5 oe7 kai2-koat jin5-lui7 choat8-bang7 e5 khou2-keng2.
Ti7 choan5 se3-kai3 bo5 koh u7 chit khoan2 e5 to7-li2, lan2 tioh8 eng7 hoaN-hi2 kap pa2-ak e5 sim, khi3 thoan5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 Hok-im, in-ui7 khak-sin3 Hok-im sit8-chai7 u7 kong-hau7. Chiu7-si7 te7-it bo5 ng3-bang7, li7-khui Siong7-te3 te7-it hng7 e5 lang5 , ti7 choe7-ok chhim-ian e5 lang5 , long2 oe7 tui3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok Hok-im e5 koan5-leng5 lai5 tit-kiu3. Sou2-i2 Po2-lo5 kong2, “In-ui7 goa2 bo5 liah8 Hok-im choe3 kian3-siau3, in-ui7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 beh kiu3 long2-chong2 sin3 e5 lang5 ” (Lo5-ma2 1:16). Hok-im i2-goa7 bo5 koh u7 i-ti7 e5 pan7-hoat, che chiah si7 lan2 tioh8 thoan5 e5 to7-li2. Siong7-te3 e5 Hok-im, chiu7-si7 jin5-lui7 e5 ng3-bang7------“Chiu7-si7 Ki-tok ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7 si2” (I Ko-lim5-to 15:3). Hok-im oe7 kai2-koat sou2 u7 e5 bun7-toe5. Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 , lan2 thang eng7 choe3 toa7 e5 khak-sin3 khi3 thoan5 chit-e5 Hok-im.
TaN, li2 na7 bo5 an2-ni chhim-sin3, ti7 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok chiu7 boe7 ku2-tng5, chiu7-si7 tioh8 beng5-pek8 jin5-lui7 ka-ki7 bo5 pan7-hoat, bo5 ng3-bang7, oan5-choan5 pho3-san2, na7 m7 sin3-kho3 Hok-im chiu7 boe7 tit-tioh8 i-ti7; na7 bo5 che khak-sin3, li2 chiu7 boe7 seng5-kong. Li2 na7 m7-sin3 jin5-lui7 sit8-chai7 pai7-hoai7, si2 ti7 in e5 ke3-sit kap choe7-koa3, ia7 li2 u7 tit-tioh8 chi2-u7 chit8 e5 i-ti7 e5 pan7-hoat------chiu7-si7 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 Hok-im, oe7 kai2-koat lang5 te7-it thang kiaN e5 cheng5-heng5, oe7 hou7 choe7-choe7 bo5 ng3-bang7--e5 u7 ng3-bang7; chiu7 li2 thoan5 Hok-im hou7 in ia7 boe7 seng5-kong.
3. Hian3-sin Ti7 Chit8-e5 Ui2-tai7 E5 Bok8-phiau
Po2-lo5 kong2, “tok8-tok8 choan-bun5 chit8 hang7,” Po2-lo5 kui-si3-lang5 teh choe3 chit8 hang7 su7 na7-tiaN7. Li2 ti7 ou3-to7 kiu3 leng5-hun5 e5 kang, na7 beh seng5-kong, tioh8 bo5 chhap pat8-mih8, kui-si3-lang5 chi2-u7 choe3 chit8 hang7 su7, ui7-tioh8 chi2-u7 chit8-e5 bok8-phiau lai5 lou2-lek8. Na7 koan-sim to-hong-bin7, u7 choe7-choe7 an3-sng3, ke3-ek8, koh ai3 chhap pat8-hang7 su7, i chiu7 choe3 poe3-to7 e5 kang ia7 boe7 seng5-kong. Ti7 jin5-seng e5 lou7-theng5 ai3 beh seng5-kong, tioh8 kui-si3-lang5 chi2-u7 chit8-e5 toa7 bok8-phiau, ui7-tioh8 che lai5 lou2-lek8.
Ti7 kiu5-hak8 e5 si5-tai7, choat8-tui3 m7-thang siuN7 beh kiat-hun; in-ui7 chit8 hong-bin7 thak8-chheh, chit8 hong-bin7 koh hu7-khi2 ka-teng5 e5 chek-jim7, ti7 keng-che3 siong7 sit8-chai7 si7 chit8-e5 chin tang7 e5 taN3. Koh an2-ni oe7 hun-sim, boe7 thang ti3-i3 hak8-giap8, thai2 oe7 ti7 i e5 su7-giap8 u7 seng5-kong? Oan5-seng5 hak8-giap8 chiah lai5 kiat-hun, kiam2 m7-si7 khah ho2 mah?
Goa2 boe7 liau2-kai2 chaiN2-iuN7 u7 e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2 chit8 hong-bin7 thoan5-to7, chit8 hong-bin7 koh teh choe3 seng-li2. Siong7-te3 ki3-jian5 tiau3 lang5 lai5 thoan5 Hok-im, i eng-kai tui3 thoan5 Hok-im lai5 oah8 chiah tioh8, i bo5 li2-iu5 tioh8 khi3 than3 tam7-poh8 chiN5. I khi3 choe3 seng-li2, au7-lai5 chiu7 koan-sim seng-li2, sou2 siuN7 e5 si7 seng-li2, chiu7 boe7 thang choan-sim thoan5-to7, in-ui7 thoan5-to7 kap seng-li2 long2 tioh8 eng7 si5-kan.
Thoan5 to7-li2 e5 kang su-iau3 choan-sim, chiah oe7 thang choe3. Si5-kan, cheng-sin5, khui3-lat8 long2 tioh8 eng7 ti7 thoan5-to7 e5 kang-chok, koh tioh8 mi5-jit8 gian2-kiu3 chiah oe7 eng7 tit. Tioh8 choat8-tui3 chin7-tiong ti7 Siong7-te3 tiau3 i lai5 choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-chok. I na7 siuN7 beh than3 tam7-poh8 chiN5, koan-sim ti7 chit8 hang7 seng-li2, i chiu7 boe7 choan-sim ti7 Siong7-te3 siat-lip8 i tioh8 choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-chok.
Siu-to7-jin5 e5 khoaN3-hoat chin tioh8; in siuN7, tioh8 koaiN ti7 siu-to7-iN7 e5 lai7-bin7, kap se3-kan bo5 kan-siap8, an2-ni chiah oe7 eng7 choan5-pou7 e5 si5-kan, ti3-i3 ti7 in e5 kang-chok. In siuN7 tioh8 pang3-sak it-chhe3 sou2 ai3 e5, bo5 chhap se3-kan chiah oe7 oan5-choan5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 . Sui-jian5 in e5 hong-hoat m7-tioh8, chong2-si7 in e5 bok8-tek kap bok8-phiau chin ho2. Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-ek8 si7 ai3 lan2 kap pat8-lang5 u7 ong2-lai5, chong2-si7 tioh8 choan-sim ti3-i3 ti7 I.
Choe3 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5, na7 bo5 choan-sim thiaN3 i e5 tiong7-hu, teh loan5-bou7 pat8-lang5, i chiu7 m7-si7 chit8-e5 ho2 lu2-tek e5; tiong7-hu na7 teh ai3 pat8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 , i ia7 m7-si7 ho2 e5 tiong7-hu. Thoan5-kau3-chia2 na7 teh keng-eng5 choe7-choe7 su7-giap8, thai2 oe7 choe3 chit8-e5 chin7-tiong e5 kang-lang5 ? Thoan5-kau3-chia2 tioh8 choe3 chit8-e5 kui-si3-lang5 u7 toa7 bok8-phiau e5 lang5 , i tioh8 kap Po2-lo5 tang5-sim kong2: “Tok8-tok8 choan-bun5 chit8 hang7”.
Po2-lo5 kong2: “KiN3-na7 chhut-kun e5 peng bo5 hou7 se3-su7 tiN5-poaN3, thang hou7 chio-bou7 i e5 hoaN-hi2” (II The5-mou5-thai3 2:4). The5-mou5-thai3 tioh8 choe3 chit8-e5 choan-sim ti3-i3 e5 lang5 . Po2-lo5 ka7 i kong2, na7 siuN7 beh choe3 chit8-e5 seng5-kong e5 peng-teng, tioh8 bo5 hou7 se3-su7 tiN5-poaN3. Thoan5-kau3-chia2 ia7 tioh8 an2-ni, i na7 beh chiau3 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3 e5 lai5 hok8-sai7 I, chiu7 m7-thang hou7 se3-su7 tiN5-poaN3, koan-sim pat8-hang7.
Li2 ai3 hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7 mah? An2-ni, li2 beh hoaN-hi2 hi-seng mah? Li2 kiam2 beh pang3-sak it-chhe3, kui-si3-lang5 choan-bun5 chit8 hang7 su7? Li2 u7 beh hong7-hian3 li2 choan5-pou7 e5 oah8-mia7, lai5 choe3 chit8 hang7 su7, bo5 iong5-un2 pat8-hang7 lai5 hun7-chap8 li2 e5 koan-sim kap chu2-i3? Li2 u7 beh chip8-tiong sim-i3, oan5-choan5 hong7-hian3 pun2-sin hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 mah? Li2 ki3-jian5 an2-ni choe3, Siong7-te3 beh ui7-tioh8 I e5 eng5-kng kap chun-kui3 lai5 eng7 li2, li2 thoan5-to7 e5 kang ia7 oe7 seng5-kong.
4.Tu5-khi3 Seng-oah8 Tiong Sou2-u7 E5 That-gai7
“Goa2 na7 sim-lai7 chu3-tiong7 choe7-ok, Chu2 tek-khak bo5 beh thiaN”. Che kiam2-chhai2 si7 Siong7-te3 bo5 beh eng7 li2 e5 goan5-in, phah-sng3 ti7 li2 e5 sim-lai7 u7 ngou2-siong7, ti7 li2 e5 iaN5-lai7 u7 A-kan. Kiam2-chhai2 u7 sim2-mih8 tang7-taN3, a2-si7 sip8-koan3 li2 m7-kheng2 pang3-sak, bo5 tiaN7-tioh8 li2 m7 seng5-jin7 che si7 choe7-ok, chong2-si7 in-ui7 che ti7 li2 kap Siong7-te3 e5 tiong-kan, ti3-kau3 Siong7-te3 boe7 thang eng7 li2.
Jit8-jit8 li2 siuN7 beh chin3-pou7, chong2-si7 u7 sim2-mih8 teh thoa li2 to3-tng2? U7 sim2-mih8 tang7-taN3 beh hou7 li2 tim5-loh8-khi3, hou7 li2 boe7 thang chiau3 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3 lai5 chau2 hit-e5 lou7-cham7? Li2 khoaN3-choe3 bo5 sim2-mih8 li7-hai7 e5 sip8-koan3 teh chou2-tong3 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 hian2-beng5 ti7 li2 e5 seng-oah8, in-ui7 li2 m7-kheng2 oan5-choan5 pang3-sak, sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 boe7 thang eng7 li2.
Choe7-ok teh chou2-tong3 li2 leng5-seng3 e5 chin3-pou7, hou7 Seng3 Sin5 iu-bun7; li2 na7 bo5 beh eng2-oan2 pang3-sak koh li7-khui, choat8-tui3 bo5 koh hong3-chhiong3, li2 e5 seng-oah8, kang-chok chiu7 boe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 kap chiok-hok. Li2 na7 ai3 choe3 chit8-e5 seng5-kong e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2, tui3 li2 sou2 choe3 e5 kang-chok hou7 lang5 hun3-heng, li2 tioh8 kap choe7-ok toan7-choat8 koan-he7.
“Siong7-te3 ah, kiu5 Li2 kam3-chhat goa2, chai goa2 e5 sim-su; Chhi3-giam7 goa2, chai goa2 e5 i3-su3. KhoaN3 goa2 u7 sim2-mih8 phaiN2 sou2-kiaN5 bo5, Chhoa7 goa2 kiaN5 eng2-oah8 e5 lou7” (Si-phian 139:23~24). Kiam2-chhai2 li2 chin u7 thian-chai5, chai5-tiau7 kap hak8-bun7, chong2-si7 ti7 li2 thoan5-to7 e5 kang-chok, oan5-choan5 sit-pai7; in-ui7 ti7 li2 e5 seng-oah8, ti7 li2 e5 sim-lai7 u7 sim2-mih8 teh hou7 Seng3 Sin5 iu-bun7, ti3-kau3 hou7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok boe7 thang chiau3 I e5 sim-i3, ui7-tioh8 I e5 eng5-kng kap chun-kui3 lai5 eng7 li2. Tioh8 hou7 Siong7-te3 kam3-chhat li2, chhi3-giam7 li2, hian2-beng5 li2 sim-lai7 e5 A-kan. Au7-lai5 jin7-choe7 hoan2-hoe2, chheng-khi3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, hou7 I chiok-hok li2 e5 kang-chok.
5. Pian7-pian7 Thang Hou7 Siong7-te3 Eng7
Kau3 taN sou2 kong2 e5, si7 siau-kek8 hong-bin7 e5 su7. Siong7-te3 choe3-toa7 e5 bok8-tek chiu7-si7 ai3 lan2 chiong it-seng oan5-choan5 kau hou7 I, I chiu7 chiau3 I e5 chi2-i3 lai5 eng7 lan2. sou2-i2 Seng3-keng chit8-pai2 koh chit8-pai2 ka3-si7 lan2 kong2: “Tioh8 chiong pun2-sin hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3 ”.
Sio-hui5 sai-hu7 beh eng7 thou5 choe3 khi3-ku7 e5 si5, thou5 na7 boe7 chiau3 sai-hu7 e5 i3-su3, chiu7 choe3 boe7 seng5. Sai-hu7 boe7 thang chiau3 i e5 i3-su3 choe3 sou2 ai3 e5 hui5, in-ui7 thou5 u7 mau5-peng7. Hit-e5 chou2-tong3 chit8-e5 tu5-khi3, thou5 chiu7 oan5-choan5 hang5-hok8 sai-hu7, i chiu7 oe7 chiaN5-choe3 sou2-ai3 e5 hui5. Li2, goa2 e5 seng-oah8 ia7 si7 an2-ni, tioh8 oan5-choan5 kau hou7 Siong7-te3 pian7-pian7 thang eng7, I e5 koan5-leng5 chiah oe7 tiam3 ti7 lan2, koh ui7-tioh8 i e5 eng5-kng kap chun-kui3 I beh eng7 lan2. I chiah oe7 chiok-hok lan2 thoan5 to7-li2 kiu3 leng5-hun5 e5 kang-chok.
Lan2 na7 iau2 u7 ka-ki7 e5 i3-su3, Siong7-te3 chiu7 boe7 choe3 sim2-mih8. I e5 chi2-i3 tioh8 piN3-choe3 lan2 e5 i3-su3, hit si5 I chiah oe7 chiok-hok lan2. An2-ni lan2 chiu7 oe7 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou saN-kap kong2: “Goa2 e5 Siong7-te3 ah, Li2 e5 chi2-i3, goa2 hoaN-hi2 than3”.
Siong7-te3 m7-si7 giam5-hat e5 chu2-lang5 , I m7-bat bian2-kiong2 lan2 khi3 choe3 sou2 m7-ai3 e5 su7. Tai7-seng I beh kam2-tong7 lan2 hou7 lan2 kam-goan7, au7-lai5 lan2 chiu7 hoaN-hi2 sun7-hok8 I. OaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, I e5 chi2-i3, chiaN5-choe3 lan2 e5 i3-su3, au7-lai5 lan2 chiu7-si7 beh sun7-hok8 I. Sou2-i2 lan2 tioh8 chiong pun2-sin oan5-choan5 kau hou7 Siong7-te3 pian7-pian7 thang eng7.
PiN7-lang5 na7 ku7-choat8 i-seng e5 i-ti7, i-seng chiu7 bo5 pan7-hoat. PiN7-lang5 tioh8 chiong pun2-sin oan5-choan5 kau hou7 i-seng, koh tioh8 chiau3 i-seng e5 chi2-to7 chiah8 ioh8, an2-ni i chiah u7 tit-tioh8 i-ho2 e5 ng3-bang7. PiN7-lang5 na7 chiau3 ka-ki7 e5 i3-su3 chiah8 i sou2 ai3 e5 ioh8-a2, bo5 beh chiap-lap8 i-seng sou2 khui e5 ioh8-a2, i-seng chiu7 boe7 thang ka7 i i-ti7. I tioh8 chiong pun2-sin oan5-choan5 kau hou7 i-seng chiah oe7 eng7-tit.
Li2, goa2 ia7 si7 an2-ni, na7 bo5 chiong pun2-sin oan5-choan5 kau hou7 Siong7-te3 pian7-pian7 thang eng7, I chiu7 boe7 thang ka7 lan2 choe3 sim2-mih8. Siong7-te3 ai3 li2 oan5-choan5 hang5-hok8 I, na7 bo5, I chiu7 choat8-tui3 boe7 boan2-chiok, tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-e5 hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7 e5 lou5-chai5, chiong pun2-sin long2 kau hou7 I, pian7-pian7 thang eng7, I chiu7 ui7-tioh8 I e5 eng5-kng beh eng7 li2.
6. Tek-seng3 E5 Ki5-to2
Nga2-kok ti7 ki5-to2 kap Siong7-te3 tau3 su-iaN5. Kin-a2-jit8, lan2 teh ki5-to2 e5 si5, chin chio2 kap Siong7-te3 tau3 su-iaN5. Lan2 cha2-khi2-si5 khi2-lai5, chiu7 kui7 ti7 bin5-chng5, chhui3-lai7 kong2 kui2-ku3 chiu7 sng3-choe3 i2-keng ki5-to2 liau2; au7-lai5 seng-khu ia3-sian7, u7-si5 an2-ni chhin3-chhai2 ki5-to2 kui2-ku3 chiu7 to2 teh khun3. Lan2 sou2 siuN7 e5 ki5-to2 chiu7-si7 chit8-khoan2.
Chong2-si7 Nga2-kok e5 ki5-to2 m7-si7 an2-ni, i kui-mi5 kap Siong7-te3 tau3 su-iaN5, au7-lai5 kong2, “Li2 na7 bo5 ka7 goa2 chiok-hok, goa2 m7 pang3 Li2 khi3.” U7 lang5 long2 m7-chai ki5-to2 chiu7-si7 kap Siong7-te3 tau3 su-iaN5, ia7 m7-chai tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 khah iaN5. Lan2 na7 bo5 khah iaN5 Siong7-te3 , chiu7 boe7 thang khah-iaN5 lang5 ; na7 beh khah-iaN5 lang5 , chiu7 tioh8 tam-tng seng-san2 e5 kan-khou2.
Chu2 Ia5-sou chai-iaN2 ti7 ki5-to2 tioh8 keng-ke3 seng-san2 e5 kan-khou2. I bat thong-mi5 ki5-to2; I e5 hak8-seng siong5-siong5 ti7 phian-phiah e5 sou2-chai7, khoaN3-tioh8 I teh kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, piaN3-chhut I e5 sim-sin5, thong3-khou2 pek-chhiat ki5-to2. Li2, goa2 bo5 sim2-mih8 chai chit-khoan2 e5 ki5-to2, chong2-si7 lan2 na7 bo5 hak8-sip8 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, ti7 ki5-to2 tam-tng seng-san2 e5 thong3-khou2, lan2 chiu7 boe7 seng5-kong. Na7 bo5 an2-ni, Siong7-te3 chiu7 boe7 thang eng7 lan2, boe7 thiaN lan2 e5 ki5-to2, ti7 lan2 e5 kang-chok eng5-kng I pun2-sin.
Cha-li2-su7 Hun-ni5 (19 se3-ki2 e5 hun3-heng-ka, Charles G. Finny) chiu7 u7 chit-khoan2 ki5-to2 e5 tang7-taN3. I si5-siong5 kau3 chhiu7-na5 lai7 a2-si7 phian-phiah e5 sou2-chai7, ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 thong3-khou2 ki5-to2, u7-si5 i boe7 thang eng7 oe7 kong2-chhut i e5 ki5-kiu5, chi2-u7 thou2-khui3 lau5 bak8-sai2, in-ui7 sim-lai7 kam2-kak ki5-to2 e5 tang7-taN3 kau3 hiah tang7. Sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 toa7-toa7 su2-iong7 i, hou7 i chiaN5-choe3 te7-it ui2-tai7 e5 hun3-heng-ka, che long2 m7 si7 thang ki5-koai3 e5 su7. Siong7-te3 pun2-sin tui3 i e5 kang-chok tit-tioh8 eng5-kng, in-ui7 i chai-iaN2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 thong3-khou2 ki5-to2.
kiN3-na7 Siong7-te3 sou2 eng7 e5 lang5 , long2 si7 ki5-to2 e5 lang5 . Li2 na7 m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7 ki5-to2, chaiN2-iuN7 kap Siong7-te3 tau3 su-iaN5, chaiN2-iuN7 thong3-khou2 ki5-to2, chiu7 iau2 m7-chai leng5-hun5 seng-san2 e5 kan-khou2, an2-ni, li2 chiu7 m7-chai beh tit-tioh8 siok8-leng5 hau7-ko2 e5 i3-gi7. Li2 na7 ai3 ti7 li2 e5 kang-chok khoaN3-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng, te7-it iau3-kin2, li2 tioh8 choe3 chit8-e5 oe7-hiau2 ki5-to2 e5 lang5 .
7. Chhiong-moa2 Siong7-te3 E5 Oe7 E5 Chit-bu7
U7 chin-choe7 bok8-su, ui7-tioh8 beh chun2-pi7 to7-li2 chiah hian-khui Seng3-keng lai5 thak8. Chit khoan2 lang5 ti7 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok boe7 thang chin3-pou7. Li2, goa2 beh hou7 leng5-seng3 chin3-pou7, long2 tioh8 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 oe7. Lan2 tioh8 chin sek8 Seng3-keng e5 loe7-iong5; beh sek8, chi2-u7 chit8-e5 hong-hoat, chiu7-si7 tioh8 thak8 i; tui3 Chhong3-se3-ki3 thak8 kau3 Khe2-si7-liok8, chit8 pai2 koh-chai3 chit8-pai2 it-tit8 thak8, teh thak8 e5 si5 tioh8 siuN7 hit-e5 i3-su3, tioh8 choe3 ki3-ho7, tioh8 gian2-kiu3, hou7 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 chhiong-moa2 li2, koh chiaN5-choe3 li2 pun2-sin e5. An2-ni, Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 chiau3 I e5 i3-su3 eng7 li2.
Siat-su2 li2 sou2 beh eng7 e5 bu2-khi3 bo5 sek8, kau3 li2 beh eng7 e5 si5, chiu7 put-li7 koh toa7 sun2-sit. Lan2 e5 bu2-khi3 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7, lan2 na7 bo5 sek8, koh m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7 eng7, chiu7 ti7 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok boe7 sun7-li7. Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 tioh8 put-si5 khng3 ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7, hou7 lan2 sui5-si5 oe7 kong2 chhut chiah tioh8. ln2 tioh8 chai-bat Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7, lai5 siuN7 i, hou7 i chiaN5-choe3 lan2 pun2-sin e5. Sou2-i2 ti7 poaN3-mi5 cheng-sin5 e5 si5, ia7 oe7-hiau2 chit8-pai2 koh chit8-pai2 am3-liam7 lai5 chhiong-moa2 i chiah tioh8. Siong7-te3 sou2 beh eng7 e5, chiu7-si7 I e5 Oe7, m7 si7 lan2 e5 oe7.
Siong7-te3 sou2 kong2 e5 Oe7 chiah u7 koan5-leng5. Lan2 tioh8 eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7, ju2 eng7 chiah oe7 ju2 bat i. Sou2-i2 goa2 beh koh kong2, lan2 tioh8 thak8 Seng3-keng kau3 i chiaN5-choe3 lan2 pun2-sin e5, in-ui7 bo5 pat8-mih8 oe7 thang thoe3-oaN7 jim7-bat Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7.
8. Tioh8 Thoan5 U7 Oah8-mia7 E5 To7-li2
Bo5-lun7 choe3 soan-kau3-su khi3 goa7-kok thoan5 to7-li2, a2-si7 choe3 thoan5-kau3-chia2 thoan5 Hok-im, na7 bo5 pa2-ak sou2 beh thoan5 e5 to7-li2, chiu7 m7-thang khi3 thoan5. Che to7-li2 chiu7-si7 “In-ui7 Siong7-te3 chiong tok8-siN e5 KiaN2 siuN2-su3 se3-kan, hou7 kiN3-na7 sin3 I e5 lang5 boe7 tim5-lun5, oe7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8; I thiaN3 se3-kan kau3 an2-ni” (Iok-han7 3:16). Li2 na7 m7 ai3 thoan5 Siong7-te3 e5 kiu3-un hou7 tim5-lun5 e5 se3-kan lang5 ; tui3 hiah e5 seng-oah8 ti7 ou-am3 e5 choe7-jin5 soan-ko3 oe7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oah8; li2 chiu7 m7-thang khi3 thoan5.
Li2 siaN2-su7 beh choe3 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 kang? Li2 teh thoan5 Chu2 e5 Hok-im, hit e5 bok8-tek si7 sim2-mih8? Ui7-tioh8 seng-oah8? KhoaN3 choe3 ko-siong7 e5 thau5-lou7? Hou7 li2 u7 mia5-siaN oe7 kam2-tong7 lang5 ?
Na7 an2-ni, li2 khah ho2 tioh8 khi3 chhe7 pat8-khoan2 e5 chit-giap8, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 boe7 thang chiok-hok li2. Li2 na7 m7-si7 beh thoan5 Siong7-te3 e5 to7-li2, beh tui3 hiah e5 seng-oah8 ti7 choe7-ok kap ou-am3 e5 lang5 thoan5 chin oah8 e5 Kiu3-chu2, koh tui3 in soan-ko3 “Ki-tok ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7 si2”, na7 bo5 beh po3 hiah-e5 tim5-lun5 e5 chai, “Li2 khoaN3, Siong7-te3 e5 iuN5-ko, chiu7-si7 tam-tng se3-kan e5 choe7 e5”, na7 bo5 beh an2-ni choe3, khah ho2 tioh8 khi3 choe3 pat8-hang7, in-ui7 thoan5-to7 e5 kang li2 bo5 hun7.
Li2 kang2-to7 liau2-au7, hou7 thiaN-chiong3 e5 in3-siong7 si7 sim2-mih8? Chin ho2 e5 ka3-si7, a2-si7 TaN goa2 chai Ia5-sou Ki-tok chin ki5-biau7! Li2 e5 bok8-tek na7-si7 beh ka3-si7, khah ho2 tioh8 pang3-sak, in-ui7 se3-kan bo5 su-iau3 ka3-si7, si7 su-iau3 u7 oah8-mia7 e5 to7-li2. U7 oah8-mia7 e5 to7-li2 kap ka3-si7 oan5-choan5 bo5 sio-siang7. Li2 oe7 thang khi3 Sin5-hak8-iN7 hak8-sip8 beh chaiN2-iuN7 ka3-si7, chong2-si7 li2 tioh8 khi3 chhe7 Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 oah8-mia7 e5 to7-li2. Ka3-si7 boe7 kam2-tong7 hoe7-iu2, chong2-si7 u7 oah8-mia7 e5 to7-li2 chiu7 oe7. Ka3-si7 kam2-hoa3 lang5 e5 ti3-sek, na7-si7 u7 oah8-mia7 e5 to7-li2 chiu7 kam2-tong7 lang5 e5 sim. Sou2-i2 lan2 tek-khak tioh8 thoan5 Ki-tok si7 chin koh si7 oah8 e5 Kiu3-chu2.
Na7-si7 ui7-tioh8 seng-oah8, than3-chiN5, mia5-siaN, toe7-ui7 lai5 hian3-sin ti7 thoan5-to7 e5, goa2 siuN7 si7 than3-cha2 li7-khui chit tiau5 thoan5-to7 e5 lou7 chiah ho2. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 e5 hok-khi3, choat8-tui3 boe7 kang3-loh8 ti7 chun5 chit-khoan2 sim e5 lang5 .
Chit se3-kan teh khiam3-eng7 thoan5 Siong7-te3 to7-li2 e5 lang5 . Li2 ti7 kang2-tai5 teh thoan5 Ki-tok, teh soan-iong5 chit ui7 chin koh si7 oah8 e5 Ki-tok, I e5 chun5-chai7 si7 ui7-tioh8 beh biat8-bong5 e5 se3-kan, an2-ni Siong7-te3 tek-khak beh chiok-hok li2, koh ui7-tioh8 I e5 eng5-kng lai5 eng7 li2. An2-ni, li2 chiu7 tam-tng te7-it toa7 e5 su2-beng7 kap kang-chok, ia7 chhim-sin3 li2 choat8-tui3 boe7 hou7-hoe2 khi2-thau5 in3-tap Siong7-te3 e5 tiau3-beng7. Kau3 li2 jin5-seng e5 kiat-kiok8, lai5 hoe5-kou3 li2 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 sou2 choe3 e5 kang, li2 chiu7 oe7 kam2-siu7 Siong7-te3 , hou7 li2 it-seng thang hok8-sai7 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok.
9. Tioh8 U7 Seng3 Sin5 E5 Iu5 Ka7 Lan2 Boah
Kin-a2-jit8 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 m7-kaN2 kong2-khi2 Seng3 Sin5 e5 tai7-chi3, in-ui7 ti7 ke3-khi3 u7 chin-choe7 lang5 tui3 Seng3 Sin5 ke3-thau5 po2-siu2, a2-si7 ke3-thau5 jiat8-kong5 lam7-sam2 sin3, sou2-i2 chiu7 m7-kaN2 koh kong2-khi2. Sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni, I si7 Sam-ui7 it-the2 e5 chin Sin5, si7 Siong7-te3 eng2-oan2 ke3-ek8 e5 chip-heng5-chia2. Ti7 Sin-iok Seng3-keng, Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 lan2 chiu7 khoaN3-kiN3 I chaiN2-iuN7 teh chi2-to7, teh choe3-kang. I in2-chhoa7, chi2-si7 su3-tou5; it-chhe3 long2 si7 I teh leng2-to7. Seng3 Sin5 kam2-tong7 lang5 chai choe7, ka7 lang5 hun3-heng. Seng3 Sin5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 , I chhong3-siat chhou-tai7 kau3-hoe7.
Kin-a2-jit8 toa7-pou7-hun7 e5 lang5 long2 hut-liok8 Seng3 Sin5. Lan2 siuN7 bo5 I e5 pang-chan7, lan2 ia7 oe7 seng5-kong; hak8-bun7, hun3-lian7 oe7 thoe3-oaN7 I e5 chun5-chai7 kap I e5 koan5-leng5, oan5-choan5 bo5 kho3 Seng3 Sin5, kho3 jiok8-the2 e5 khui3-lat8 lou2-lek8 teh choe3-kang. TaN hian7-chai7 chiu7-si7 lan2 tioh8 hou7 Seng3 Sin5 tit I goan5-lai5 te7-ui7 e5 si5, in-ui7 I tek-khak tioh8 choe3-kang. Li2, goa2 tioh8 chai-iaN2, Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 beh eng7 iu5 boah lan2; na7 bo5, ti7 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 e5 su7, lan2 chiu7 boe7 oan5-choan5.
KiN3-na7 Siong7-te3 sou2 eng7 e5 lang5 , long2 u7 tit-tioh8 Seng3 Sin5 eng7 iu5 boah in. Tak8 e5 pou3-to7-ka ti7 in e5 seng-oah8 long2 u7 tu2-tioh8 gui5-ki, na7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 chiu7 lai5 choe3 Chu2 koan2-li2 in, eng7 in. Lek8-tai7 hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7 e5 lang5 , long2 oe7 liau2-kai2 Seng3 Sin5 eng7 iu5 boah in e5 i3-gi7, in choat8-tui3 boe7 boan2-chiok sou2 siu7 e5 kau3-iok8 kap hun3-lian7. In-ui7 chai-iaN2 chiah e5 i2-goa7, iau2 koh su-iau3 pat8-hang7, chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 eng7 iu5 boah in, Siong7-te3 chiah oe7 eng7 in. Sou2-i2 in chiu7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 theng3-hau7 kau3 tit-tioh8 tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 e5 koan5-leng5, au7-lai5 chiu7 chhut-khi3, ti7 kui2 le2-pai3, kui2 geh8 jit8 hian2-beng5 Seng3 Sin5 e5 koan5-leng5 lai5 choe3-kang, ia7 sou2 oan5-seng5 e5 kang si7 pi2 in kho3 jiok8-the2 e5 khui3-lat8 choe3 chit8 ni5 koh-khah choe7.
Siong7-te3 kin-a2-jit8 ai3 beh eng7 iu5 boah lang5 , li2 na7 m7-chai goa2 hian7-chai7 teh ka7 li2 kong2, na7 bo5 Seng3 Sin5 e5 iu5, ti7 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 kang-chok, li2 chiu7 boe7 chin seng5-kong.
Chit hang7 su7 m7 si7 hou7 li2 piN3-choe3 jiat8-kong5 e5 sin3-giong2. Tak8 hang7 long2 u7 tiong-iong5 chi to7, bo5 chau2 ti7 liong2 kek8-toan. Li2 thang chiau3 Seng3-keng sou2 ka3-si7 lan2, ia7 si7 chu7-kou2 i2-lai5 Siong7-te3 e5 lou5-pok8 sou2 seng5-jin7 e5, lai5 tit-tioh8 che keng-giam7. Li2 na7 sit8-chai7 khoaN3-tang7 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 e5 su7, li2 tek-khak beh siuN7 pan7-hoat lai5 tit-tioh8 che keng-giam7, hou7 li2 ia7 chiaN5-choe3 Siong7-te3 eng7 iu5 boah e5 lang5 .
Li2 na7 ai3 hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7, ti7 li2 e5 kang-chok hou7 choe7-jin5 chai choe7, hoan2-hoe2, li2 tioh8 ti7 I e5 bin7-cheng5 theng3-hau7 tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 e5 koan5-leng5, chhin-chhiuN7 saN ka7 li2 chheng7. Li2 chiu7 beh chiaN5-choe3 Siong7-te3 eng7 iu5 boah e5 lang5 .
10. Tioh8 U7 Sin3-sim Teh Ki5-thai7 Theng3-hau7
Eng-kok e5 hun3-heng-ka, Su Pou3-chin u7 chit8-pai2 phai3 i e5 hak8-seng ti7 Lun5-tun e5 choe7-choe7 tiau5 koe-lou7 piN khui pou3-to7-hoe7. Hak8-seng tak8-jit8 tng2-lai5 po3-ko3, u7 e5 seng5-kong, u7 e5 bo5. U7 chit8-jit8 chit e5 un-su3, chai5-tiau7 khah chio2 e5 chheng-lian5-lang5 , chin sit-chi3 lai5 kiN3 Su Pou3-chin kong2, Su Pou3-chin Sian-siN, goa2 boe7 liau2-kai2 siaN2-su7 goa2 boe7 tit-tioh8 lang5 sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, goa2 u7 hun7 ti7 koe-lou7 piN pou3-to7 e5 kang, chin7-tiong thoan5 Hok-im, koh chin7 goa2 choe3 toa7 e5 lou2-lek8 teh choe3-kang, chong2-si7 goa2 teh chhiaN2 lang5 lai5 sin3 Chu2 e5 si5, chiu7 bo5 sim2-mih8 hoan2-eng3, na7 u7 ia7 chin-chio2. Su Pou3-chin liah8 i khoaN3, au7-lai5 chiah tui3 i kong2, Li2 siuN7, tak8-pai2 li2 teh thoan5 to7-li2 e5 si5, choan5-leng5 e5 Siong7-te3 beh chin2-kiu3 lang5 ? Hit-e5 chheng-lian5 chiah chhiN2-ngou7 kong2, Bo5, goa2 m7-kaN2 an2-ni ki5-thai7, goa2 ti7 hak8-hau7 e5 hun3-lian7 iau2-be7 oan5-seng5, goa2 e5 un-su3 kap chai5-tiau7 m7 tat8-tioh8 pat8-lang5 . TaN goa2 chai goa2 e5 chho3-gou7, goa2 m7 eng-kai an2-ni ki5-thai7. Li2 na7 bo5 teh ki5-thai7 hau7-ko2, chiu7 boe7 tit-tioh8.
Li2 chiuN7 kang2-tai5 teng2 beh thoan5 Hok-im e5 si5, chiu7 tioh8 khak-sin3 u7 hau7-ko2, tek-khak u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 beh hoan2-hoe2 chiap-lap8 Ia5-sou Ki-tok choe3 Kiu3-chu2.
Tui3 goa2 khai-si2 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 kang-chok i2-lai5, goa2 ti7 kang2-to7 soah, chiu7 chhiaN2 lang5 lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou, hou7 thiaN-chiong3 u7 ki-hoe7 thang piau2-si7 in e5 koat-sim. Sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 boe7 li2-kai2, choe3 chit8 e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2, thoan5 Hok-im, kang2-to7 soah, chiu7 chiok-to2 soaN3-hoe7, tng2-khi3 chhu3, bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 sim2-mih8 hau7-ko2, liah8-choe3 an2-ni chiu7 kau3-giah8. Che si7 thang kiaN e5 su7. Thoan5-to7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chiah8-mih8 pai5 ti7 toh-teng2, tioh8 hou7 lang5 u7 ki-hoe7, chhiaN2 in lai5 hiong2-siu7; goa2 na7 bo5 an2-ni choe3, chiu7-si7 ti7 goa2 e5 kang-chok boe7 ki3-tit choe3 chit8-hang7 chin tiong7-iau3 e5 su7.
Goa2 tak8 le2-pai3-jit8 ti7 kang2-to7 soah, long2 u7 kio3 lang5 tioh8 hoan2-hoe2, chiap-lap8 Ki-tok choe3 Kiu3-chu2, koh hou7 leng5-seng3 tui7-loh8 e5 sin3-tou5 u7 ki-hoe7 thang hoan2-hoe2. Kui-ni5 tiong m7-bat u7 chit8-e5 le2-pai3 am3 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 hau7-ko2; chiah e5 lang5 chhut-lai5 piau2-si7 in e5 hoan2-hoe2 i2-au7, chiu7 u7 ko3-jin5 tam5-to7 jin5-oan5 chit8-e5 chit8-e5 phoaN7 in kau3 tam5-to7-sek, ti7 hia koh siong5-se3 kap in tam5-to7. Sou2-i2 na7 bo5 kiat-ko2, goa2 chiu7 chin tioh8-kiaN; in-ui7 goa2 thoan5 Hok-im, chhiaN2 lang5 lai5 hoan2-hoe2, na7 bo5 kiat-ko2, goa2 tek-khak beh ki5-koai3. Goa2 ki3-jian5 u7 thoan5, chiu7 teh ki5-thai7 u7 hau7-ko2.
Goa2 m7-si7 kong2, kiN3-na7 chhut-lai5 piau2-si7 koat-sim e5 lang5 long2 u7 tit-kiu3. Chong2-si7 ti7 in tiong-kan u7 lang5 tit-tioh8 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, ia7 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5. Goa2 khia7 ti7 kang2-tai5 beh kang2-to7 e5 si5, Siong7-te3 chiu7 hou7 goa2 u7 sin3-sim teh ki5-thai7, chiu7-si7 goa2 sou2 teh ka7 li2 kong2 e5, sou2-i2 goa2 chiu7 khak-sin3 ti7 goa2 kang2-to7 soah, chhiaN2 lang5 lai5 hoan2-hoe2 e5 si5, tek-khak u7 hoan2-eng3.
11. Oan5-choan5 Ti3-i3 Ti7 Siong7-te3 E5 Eng5-kng.
Li2 teh hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 e5 bok8-tek, na7 m7-si7 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng, iau2 koh u7 pat8 e5 bok8-tek chiu7 bo5 sim2-mih8 i3-su3. Li2 choe3 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 kang, na7-si7 ui7-tioh8 beh tui3 che lai5 tit-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 li7-ek, beh the5-ko mia5-siaN, phin2-keh, te7-ui7, lai5 tou5-bou5 ka-ki7 e5 seng-oah8; sui-jian5 ti7 goa7-piau2 u7 seng5-kong, chong2-si7 li2 choat8-tui3 boe7 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 chiok-hok. Beh eng5-kng Siong7-te3 i2-goa7, na7 iau2 koh u7 pat8 khoan2 e5 tong7-ki, li2 chiu7 boe7 thang tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 goan5-lai5 beh hou7 li2 e5 hau7-ko2. Sou2-i2 li2 teh hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 , tek-khak tioh8 ui7-tioh8 I e5 eng5-kng.
